270
00:12:46,875 --> 00:12:48,375
[ASHIYA] So you
understand me now?

271
00:12:48,458 --> 00:12:49,583
[EMI] If you mean,

272
00:12:49,666 --> 00:12:51,041
do I understand that
"His Majesty's" as much

