fresh from the salon.

294
00:13:36,375 --> 00:13:38,541
[EMI] And those
boots are new, too.

295
00:13:38,625 --> 00:13:40,250
[ASHIYA] Oh? How can you tell?

296
00:13:40,333 --> 00:13:43,000
