308
00:14:00,583 --> 00:14:01,833
[EMI] Just forget it!

309
00:14:01,916 --> 00:14:04,125
Back to the matter at hand.

310
00:14:04,208 --> 00:14:06,416
Do you think he can get
anything useful out of her?

311
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:07,500
[ASHIYA] Don't ask me.

312
00:14:07,583 --> 00:14:08,791
