[EMI] You're here,
so you fail by default.

315
00:14:14,083 --> 00:14:15,916
[EMI] Still, this whole
earthquake thing

316
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:18,791
is definitely a
cause for concern.

317
00:14:18,875 --> 00:14:20,250
One thing I know for sure;

318
00:14:20,333 --> 00:14:23,291
I'm not going to sit here
and find out the hard way.

319
00:14:23,375 --> 00:14:25,666
Not really any point in
spying on 'em from out here.

320
00:14:25,750 --> 00:14:27,000
Follow me in.

321
00:14:27,083 --> 00:14:28,333
[ASHIYA] Follow you in where?

322
00:14:28,416 --> 00:14:30,458
To get a table.
Now are you comin' or not?

323
00:14:30,541 --> 00:14:32,041
Wait a second!

324
00:14:32,125 --> 00:14:35,000
