to excuse such extreme audacity?

325
00:14:35,083 --> 00:14:39,416
No! Stop right there!

326
00:14:45,291 --> 00:14:46,500
[MAOU] Maybe you
could just go over

327
00:14:46,583 --> 00:14:48,416
the details one
more time, please.

328
00:14:48,500 --> 00:14:50,250
Yeah. Sure.

329
00:14:50,333 --> 00:14:53,583
I told you how my tinnitus
got really bad, didn't I?

330
00:14:53,666 --> 00:14:54,750
It happened right
around the time

331
00:14:54,833 --> 00:14:57,083
I started working at MgRonalds.

332
00:14:57,166 --> 00:14:58,541
At first, I thought
I was just tired

333
