335
00:15:05,583 --> 00:15:07,625
[MALE VOICE in Ente Islan]

336
00:15:07,708 --> 00:15:10,291
Hmm...?
[MALE VOICE in Ente Islan]

337
00:15:10,375 --> 00:15:12,291
Someone there?
[MALE VOICE in Ente Islan]

338
00:15:12,375 --> 00:15:17,041
Hello? Hm?
[MALE VOICE in Ente Islan]

339
00:15:17,125 --> 00:15:19,708
Hey. I can hear you.
[MALE VOICE in Ente Islan]

340
00:15:19,791 --> 00:15:21,250
[MALE VOICE in Ente Islan]

341
