[MALE VOICE in Ente Islan]

342
00:15:23,291 --> 00:15:28,041
[MALE VOICE in Ente Islan]

343
00:15:28,125 --> 00:15:30,166
Wait, a "big one"?
[MALE VOICE in Ente Islan]

344
00:15:30,250 --> 00:15:31,750
Uhhh...
[MALE VOICE in Ente Islan]

345
00:15:31,833 --> 00:15:35,250
[MALE VOICE in Ente Islan]

346
00:15:36,125 --> 00:15:37,750
Not only could I
hear what he said,

347
00:15:37,833 --> 00:15:39,458
but I understood him.

348
00:15:39,541 --> 00:15:41,541
So you can see why I'm confused.

349
00:15:41,625 --> 00:15:42,708
[MAOU] Yeah.

350
00:15:42,791 --> 00:15:43,833
And because of the
quakes we've had lately,

351
00:15:43,916 --> 00:15:45,250
you assume they're
the disturbances

352
00:15:45,333 --> 00:15:46,666
he was referring to?

353
00:15:46,750 --> 00:15:48,791
Yeah.

354
00:15:48,875 --> 00:15:50,166
[MAOU] The Idea Link.

355
00:15:50,250 --> 00:15:52,375
A method of communication
where beings

356
00:15:52,458 --> 00:15:54,333
in different worlds tune
their minds to each other

357
00:15:54,416 --> 00:15:57,125
and share impressions
and concepts.

358
00:15:57,208 --> 00:15:59,083
They're able to transfer
these ideas across time

359
00:15:59,166 --> 00:16:02,500
and space by utilizing
sonar probe technology.

360
00:16:02,583 --> 00:16:04,458
