recent earthquakes.

365
00:16:14,166 --> 00:16:16,416
And if that's true,

366
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:18,250
given the number
of quakes we've had,

367
00:16:18,333 --> 00:16:20,250
the only possible
explanation is that somebody

368
00:16:20,333 --> 00:16:24,458
