down me and Emilia.

369
00:16:24,541 --> 00:16:27,291
A big one
is coming soon indeed.

370
00:16:27,375 --> 00:16:30,166
Things are happening
faster than I expecte--

371
00:16:30,250 --> 00:16:31,875
[splutters]

372
00:16:31,958 --> 00:16:33,375
[CHIHO] What's the
matter, Mister Maou?

373
00:16:33,458 --> 00:16:34,541
Are you all right?

374
00:16:34,625 --> 00:16:35,833
[MAOU thinking] Oh, come on!

375
00:16:35,916 --> 00:16:38,458
What is Emi doing walking
in here with Ashiya?

376
00:16:38,541 --> 00:16:39,500
