377
00:16:39,583 --> 00:16:40,500
[MAOU] Nothing.

378
00:16:40,583 --> 00:16:42,416
I haven't done anything wrong.

379
00:16:42,500 --> 00:16:43,500
Huh?

380
00:16:43,583 --> 00:16:45,791
So anyway. To wrap this up.

381
00:16:45,875 --> 00:16:48,041
The tinnitus and weird voices
you've been hearing aren't

