difference, don't you?

387
00:17:00,875 --> 00:17:01,833
I'm glad I built up the nerve

388
00:17:01,916 --> 00:17:03,833
to actually ask you about this.

389
00:17:03,916 --> 00:17:06,583
I feel a million
times better already.

390
00:17:06,666 --> 00:17:07,916
[MAOU thinking] Hear that, Emi?

391
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:10,166
I'm doing a good thing here!

392
00:17:10,250 --> 00:17:13,750
Anyone can see I'm just
trying to help this girl out!

393
00:17:13,833 --> 00:17:15,791
