394
00:17:15,875 --> 00:17:17,583
Or school friends, either.

395
00:17:17,666 --> 00:17:19,875
That's why-- Well,
I guess I knew you'd

396
00:17:19,958 --> 00:17:21,791
be the only one
who'd believe me.

397
00:17:21,875 --> 00:17:24,416
You're kind, and so gentle.

398
00:17:24,500 --> 00:17:26,458
I love talking to you.

399
00:17:27,166 --> 00:17:28,541
See. Thing is.

400
00:17:28,625 --> 00:17:30,708
You're real nice and--uh.

401
00:17:30,791 --> 00:17:33,500
I uhh--Well,
Mister Maou, I like-

402
00:17:33,583 --> 00:17:35,166
