417
00:18:03,041 --> 00:18:04,166
You need to calm down too, Chi!

418
00:18:04,250 --> 00:18:07,166
No, Mister Maou,
I won't calm down!

419
00:18:07,250 --> 00:18:08,625
I remember you.

420
00:18:08,708 --> 00:18:11,166
You came into our restaurant
a couple days ago, right?

421
00:18:11,250 --> 00:18:12,375
