451
00:19:16,583 --> 00:19:18,333
[CHIHO] Where's Mister Maou?

452
00:19:18,416 --> 00:19:21,291
[EMI] Not with us, I can
tell you that much for sure.

453
00:19:21,375 --> 00:19:23,791
[CHIHO] Yeah, but do
you think he's okay?

454
00:19:23,875 --> 00:19:25,750
[EMI] Oh. You're worried
he got crushed

