492
00:20:54,375 --> 00:20:55,833
[EMI] You'll get it.

493
00:20:55,916 --> 00:21:00,208
But, in reality, maybe
it's better if you don't.

494
00:21:00,291 --> 00:21:04,500
For now. Rest up.
You could use a little sleep.

495
00:21:10,541 --> 00:21:12,041
[EMI] I hear you breathing.

496
00:21:12,125 --> 00:21:14,083
She's asleep; you can come out!

497
00:21:14,166 --> 00:21:17,083
[rocks tumbling]

498
00:21:17,166 --> 00:21:19,750
[DEEP VOICE]
Stay outta my business!

499
00:21:19,833 --> 00:21:23,125
[EMI] Maou? What
happened to your body?

500
00:21:23,208 --> 00:21:26,166
[MAOU] Don't know.
It just changed on me.

501
00:21:27,875 --> 00:21:30,666
[EMI thinking]
His magic. It's back.

502
00:21:30,750 --> 00:21:32,541
[MAOU] Man. This is the worst.

503
00:21:32,625 --> 00:21:34,625
How'm I supposed
to explain this?

504
00:21:34,708 --> 00:21:35,625
[EMI thinking] This is it.

505
00:21:35,708 --> 00:21:37,250
Now's my chance.

506
00:21:37,333 --> 00:21:40,250
If I focus all of the
celestial force I have left.

507
00:21:40,333 --> 00:21:42,208
I can still make a
Sacred Sword strong enough

508
00:21:42,291 --> 00:21:43,916
to defeat him!

509
00:21:44,541 --> 00:21:46,125
[MAOU] Take care of Chi.

510
00:21:46,208 --> 00:21:47,958
These people need me.

511
00:21:48,041 --> 00:21:50,041
Hopefully there
aren't many casualties.

512
00:21:50,125 --> 00:21:53,000
But we don't have time to
wait for the rescue squad.

513
00:21:53,083 --> 00:21:55,416
I'll figure something out.

514
00:21:56,333 --> 00:21:58,458
[EMI thinking] Is he serious?

515
00:22:00,916 --> 00:22:03,583
[MAOU] Alright. It's time to go.

516
00:22:04,416 --> 00:22:06,791
[EMI thinking] What? Why?

517
00:22:06,875 --> 00:22:09,333
Why would the
Devil rescue humans?

